0010 REM "GLE - Journal Entry (Detail Lines)"
0020 REM "Program GLE.CC"
0022 REM "+-----------------------------------------------------------+"
0024 REM "| ADD+ON Software, Inc. Advantage/V Version 6.0.0 - 15May96 |"
